{"type": "article", "id": 43752, "title": "H&M 新品牌 ARKET 完整公开，以及，Justin Bieber 推出了个纯白T恤系列 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2017-08-04T03:50:41Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 1782, "name": "Coach"}, {"id": 12303, "name": "Pokémon"}, {"id": 41377, "name": "Arket"}, {"id": 42972, "name": "ISETAN"}, {"id": 686, "name": "adidas"}, {"id": 1060, "name": "H&M"}, {"id": 2211, "name": "Tod's"}, {"id": 20675, "name": "Avon"}, {"id": 5877, "name": "Justin Bieber"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 46, "image": "img/article/article_show/20170804101712iZ8yMJw0XhasWxVt.jpg", "contents": "<h3 nocleanhtml=\"true\">一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/gadfly/articles/2017-08-03/avon-sherilyn-mccoy-resigns-miracle-worker-needed\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>雅芳 CEO Sheri McCoy 下台</strong></a> | 财报显示，Avon 集团第二季度的销售额同比下跌 3%，至 14 亿美元，净亏损从去年的 3600 万美元扩大至 4600 万美元。其首席执行官 Sheri McCoy 将于明年 3 月31 日正式离职，其接替人选待定。在过去 5 年里，由于经营不力，该公司卖掉了其美国业务，规模缩小到原来的一半，股价也下跌了 85%。<br></p><p><a href=\"http://www.reuters.com/article/us-tods-results-strategy-idUSKBN1AJ31C\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>意大利奢侈品集团 Tod’s 发布半年财报，称将专注于长期增长</strong></a> | 在截至 6 月 30 日的上半年内，Tod’s 集团销售额同比下跌 2.9% 至 4.83 亿欧元，净利润则减少 7.2% 至 3471 万欧元。其中，占比 80％ 以上的鞋履部门销售额同比下跌 3.5% 至 3.86 亿欧元，核心品牌 Tod’s 销售额则下滑 6.1% 至 2.65 亿欧元，Roger Vivier 实现了最大增幅 11%，销售额为 9260 万欧元。该集团的首席财务官 Emilio Macellari 称，集团将放弃与时尚品牌的竞争，转而强调传统、经典的产品，以追求更可靠的市场。</p><p><a href=\"http://fortune.com/2017/08/03/adidas-sales-growth-america-china/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>adidas 发布第二季度财报，中国和北美市场增长最快</strong></a> | 财报显示，在截至 6 月 30 日的三个月内，adidas 集团销售额同比增长 19% 至 50.38 亿欧元，核心品牌 adidas 销售额增幅达 21%，健身品牌 Reebok 销售额上涨了5%。另外，adidas 在中国和北美分别实现了 28% 和 26％ 的增长，但在原本强劲的俄罗斯市场的销售额下跌了 11%。</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p><a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/8/hm-arket-first-menswear-collection\" rel=\"nofollow\">H&amp;M 旗下新品牌 ARKET 首个系列完整公开</a>，这个号称要“兼具功能性与持续性设计北欧传统”的品牌坚持极简的色调和剪裁，看起来和 COS 有些相似。首个系列包括大衣、西装外套、连帽外套、马甲、高领衫、针织衫、衬衫、T-Shirt、钱包和皮鞋，定价从 19 至 250 英镑不等。 </p><p>该系列将于 8 月 25 日，ARKET 在伦敦摄政街的首个旗舰店开幕之际正式上架。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170804105042YCTESqrczuZao9Ht.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666016\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201708041050426rDRtUFkJZAvo05L.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666016\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170804105054f97Dnrzl1YjXCPUp.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666016\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170804105054G6uQBMcXeqSmjg8a.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666016\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170804105054Su4eyfmOUN03FrZx.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666016\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170804105055aW8iumVKNn9zF0dl.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666016\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170804105055kbVKwFp4LPjRqHQd.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666016\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2017080410505540SrvUXixH8C3ZRB.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666016\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170804105055Vai0GDyMplNvFTgE.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666016\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2017080410505591nybp3rjuAdTl0K.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666016\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170804105056BRdV6YgTwzCrF9xp.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666016\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170804105056uh3ZiajfsKTzblFe.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666016\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170804105056k7ICYmX2nyD1WPGj.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666016\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170804105057L6qxO1a5ksf73Cez.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666016\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2017080410505754hlXNi6TqouGnxF.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666016\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170804105057AN3QD7JotvhdEUPS.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666016\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170804105058nqZw1dHOBaQ3JDhW.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666016\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201708041050580U1jNvZTGer3MOCI.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666016\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170804105058QdqIEzDr8kgHGxam.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666016\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170804105058wYf5ypEhGazs30WB.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666016\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170804105058nXv5AKJ71egV8Pb2.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666016\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170804105059SE5GjuabwhKI7RtV.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666016\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170804105059XZFo0HQhPm5SKOcb.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666016\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>之前我们曾报道过 Lofree 的复古机械式键盘，这次，它又推出了一款名为 <a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/8/lofree-poison-speaker\" rel=\"nofollow\">Poison Speaker 的无线扬声器</a>，这款扬声器以 50 年代的收音机为灵感设计，可以持续播放 6 小时。目前正在<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/142504465/lofree-poison-nostalgic-powerful-wireless-speaker\" rel=\"nofollow\"> Kickstarter </a>上募资生产，售价为 64 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170804105004bNshdYScWXguyaF4.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667500\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170804105004DrWbzkISX64AcBfR.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666176\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201708041050178mYAdBf0vTI2aZCj.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667500\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170804105005amtT2YoS3dhHsGUE.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667112\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170804105004dx0qMEYWV4ODZfR6.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>最近，<a href=\"http://popbee.com/fashion/fashion-news/coach-art-of-expression-limited-exhibition-pre-fall-collection-2017/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Coach 在香港 IFC 连卡佛开设了 ART OF EXPRESSION 期间限定店铺</a>。这家店按照 1：1 的比例仿制了纽约地铁，用马赛克做了墙壁，车厢里也满是 Coach 的广告和涂鸦，还挺有趣的。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170804104939RHJKLsBeIhVjUu4z.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170804104939Aj5ZUkPgbVYtI4W1.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170804104939hk7aBe6JUIyNL8Gf.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170804104939jHh2IdtuwLb3DvCg.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170804104944rucVH90s1qyTonNf.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170804104944YRHZ7faGvF94JcDq.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170804104949sMxwaIy4l7B2R9uD.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>哥本哈根时尚名店 Wood Wood 庆祝成立 15 周年，与 adidas Originals 合作推出了<a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/8/wood-wood-adidas-originals-collaboration-lookbook\" rel=\"nofollow\">联名系列</a>。</p><p>该系列包括一双采用了毛绒麂皮制造的 Gazelle 鞋款，T-Shirt、帽款与围巾等服饰单品，将于 8 月 10 日正式发售。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201708041048311oIqVhCDRilJYL67.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170804104832eMqWzGhnCLx43iUj.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170804104833e0LzVU52GOplsNMm.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170804104831tqdulZNLr5phHFfR.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170804104831vEKm9PFVC1pTZ34J.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170804104834HDzqXQ9YL3NyU7xI.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170804104834UsVQbn2S1zojT9Yt.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170804104835ZsURaqC9NFmOVeHr.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170804104835zF26my9ojeSwQGUT.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170804104839RKvFwJpMQobtljCB.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.501000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2017080410483921c0rPU7EeO8nvgf.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170804104839aWR1ybwrIo4MPQ2B.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170804104844EZvF1KqNslhzQtOe.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170804104852W1xHhZpiwc9fkTXt.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>以美国经典内衣品牌 Hanes 为蓝本，Justin Bieber 最近与他的造型师 Karla Welch 推出了一个<a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/8/justin-bieber-karla-welch-t-shirt\" rel=\"nofollow\">纯白色的 T 恤系列</a>，首波单品将在洛杉矶 Maxfield 期间限定店率先发售。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170804104918UiyNGpvQ2jWl6RMJ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170804104914BcU4WCPAMub65ftq.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170804104915PIS8UTEQDGFp13e2.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170804104913tsMR5H3Av7zfw6SU.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201708041049142xRdZcwGgFmXhzLv.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201708041049148wj5fgkWZJTmlqvh.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170804104914M0xlUoW4bzLp6Tuj.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>8 月 16 日至 21 日，POKEMON 联手东京新宿的伊势丹总店，将在伊势丹百货商场的七楼，推出一个虚构的商店“<a href=\"https://www.wwdjapan.com/455454\" rel=\"nofollow\">ISETAN IN POKEMON</a>”，现场不仅有食物，还会贩售一系列公仔、地图、零钱包等单品。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201708041047477W9ZfTqX13bLevJs.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.757500\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170804104753nce3mUaC2DuyHVBO.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170804104753nmeLCR8QhYOkrJjp.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201708041047533vOD46dxLtiymjqY.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201708041047549pjyta4i1Kw3IZHT.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.706667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170804104757psbtBcgUxPLk01An.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201708041048016vB1LSACg4p3Ybf0.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170804104808sKCvZltd05Dyu4BF.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.115312\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170804104808tjlq2UEDGiSA5bFh.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.955000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201708041048082d3TNmbIVC1q0O6Q.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.950476\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><br></p><p>题图来自：<a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/8/lofree-poison-speaker\" rel=\"nofollow\">hypebeast</a>、ARKET</p>"}